@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### GET /users/:id — first call hits the fake DB (~300ms), second is instant (cached for 10s)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

###

### GET /users/:id — same id again, served from cache
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1

###

### GET /users/:id — different id, cache miss
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/2

###

### DELETE /users/:id — evict user 1 from cache
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/1

###

### GET /users/:id — cache was evicted, hits the DB again
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/1
